Fang flew to Havana from Washington , where he ended a five - day visit to the United States .
In San Diego on Tuesday ( May 13 ) , he toured the aircraft carrier USS Ronald Reagan and the combat ship USS Coronado .
He also observed Marine training at Camp Pendleton and met with the commander of the U.S. Pacific Command , Navy Adm. Samuel J. Locklear 3rd .
